title: Winter City Ornament Holidays Cards
description:
The artist of this design, Carmen Ordonez, says "I believe that if you strive for what you believe in, you will accomplish many things. This is what I go by in life.". These unique holiday cards were created by a student employed in the Marwen Foundation career development programs. Marwen is an after-school arts organization that provides high-quality visual arts, college planning, and career development programs--all free of charge--to Chicago's under-served young people.
  • Dimensions: Cards 5 x 7 in.
  • Materials: Box set of 12 cards w/envelopes
  • Inside Message: Warm wishes to you and your family this holiday season.
